handle.sh

	- handles generated alerts. For example, you may put this in: /etc/darqios/alerts/handle.sh
	- You would then symlink /etc/darqios/alerts/{clear.sh,low.sh,med.sh,high.sh} to the handle.sh script


nodemailer.js

	- simple script to mail an alert to a group of people
	- npm install nodemailer
	- In the above example, this would go in /etc/darqios/alerts/nodemailer.js
